data.description: Great investment opportunity. The property needs a new roof, new A/Cs, and some tender loving care (TLC), yet it is priced accordingly. CASH BUYERS ONLY DUE TO CONDITION. The beautiful floor plan features high-volume ceilings with a lake and pool. In the main areas There is one bedroom and a full cabana bath on the first floor, while additional bedrooms are located on the second floor. Enjoy a dual lake view in the front and back of the property. Upstairs windows come with accordion shutters, and there is a 3-car garage.The property is centrally located in Boynton Beach, offering a vibrant lifestyle with numerous restaurants, shopping centers, and easy access to highways. It provides an easy commute to nearby cities, including Delray Beach, Boca Raton and Fort Lauderdale. Both Palm Beach International Airport and Fort Lauderdale International Airport are just a short car ride away. Beachgoers will relish spending a day in the sun on the stunning shores of the Atlantic Ocean. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity
